ActIncome Tax Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS (PART LXXXIX) by replacing section 8900, by replacing the English translation of the name of a non-governmental international organization with its legal name, by adding the World Anti-doping Agency to that section, and by adding section 8901, which prescribes certain partnerships for the purposes of paragraph 249.1(1)(b) of the Act.
